	It is the second serious knee injury that Guillen has sustained.  
He tore the posterior cruciate ligament in his left knee at Oakland 
on Sept. 17 and missed the final two weeks of last season. 
</P>
<P>
	Guillen was placed on the 15-day disabled list and the Mariners  
recalled Giomar Guevera, 26, from Tacoma. They also signed Domingo 
Cedeno, a 31-year-old free agent, to a one-year contract. 
</P>
