Coast League, both at shortstop, and started Sunday's game against 
the Athletics. 
</P>
<P>
	Cedeno, 31, spent spring training with Oakland and hit .140. To  
make room, the Mariners optioned reliever Eric Weaver to Tacoma. He 
appeared in two games for the Mariners, pitching a scoreless inning 
against the A's on Saturday. 
</P>
