<HEADLINE> Olazabal Gets Same Old Jacket  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	AUGUSTA, Ga. (AP) -- Jose Maria Olazabal got the same old green  
jacket when he won the Masters for the second time today. 
</P>
<P>
	Olazabal was asked if he was wearing the same jacket that he  
received when he won the Masters in 1994. 
</P>
<P>
	``Yep, it's the same one,'' Olazabal said with a smile.  
</P>
<P>
	How did he know?  
</P>
<P>
	``Because the name is still misspelled inside,'' he said.  
</P>
<P>
	Sure enough, it was spelled ``Olazabel.''  
</P>
